@NODE "Battle Zeque Moves"
 Battle Zeque Moves
--------------------

Quick in-game-keys:

Y - attack

B - jump (hit it two times to jump higher)

Y+B - special attack

R,L - block

X - magic

Individual attacks:

Puple hair dude:  when jumping, press down and Y for step attack.

Red hair dude:  down-forward + Y for slide attack.

Yellow hair dude:  when jumping, press down and Y for knee attack.
@ENDNODE
