@NODE "Furi Furi Girls Moves"
                                 Furi Furi Girls Moves
                                 ---------------------
When start the game, choose how many human players (1-4) and computer players
(0-4).  The four characters must be all in the game.

After, select the character.  Each character has different strength.  (attack
level, life bar, gold)

Then select stage.  There are 3 different stages from easy to hard.

While in game, each character takes turn and move around on the game board.

3 things you can do when it is your turn:

                        O     Dice      - Throw the dice
                                          (after, choose the direction you
                                           want to go)

                        O     Status    - Status of 4 main characters

                        O     View      - View the play board, use direction
                                          keys for scrolling.

Your goal is to reach to boss and take the key.
@ENDNODE
