            You want to change your little guys suit?
               Well, heres how!

           When you start, you will get a display that indicates wether
           you want to start, options, or password. Anytime during this
           screen press either the ( L ) or ( R ) button.

           If Press ( R ) Button - You will be able to change the colors
                                   of the shorts and the outline.

           If Press ( L ) Button - You will be able to change the colors
                                   of the shirt and the socks.

           Colors Available      - RED + YELLOW + GREEN + DARK GREEN + BLACK
                                   WHITE + GRAY + ORANGE + DARK ORANGE + BLUE
                                   DARK BLUE + REAL DARK BLUE + PURPLE +
                                   DARK RED.
            
            Are You tired of this game? How about a game of Pong?

            At the Begin with the Illusion screen press (R) - (L) - (SELECT) 
            and thanx to Illusion you van play a peaceful game of PONG. 
            Yeah!

