@NODE "Batman Returns Codes & Walktrough"
BATMAN RETURNS  (SUPER NINTENDO)

CODES:

9 LIVES - ( go to rest on options screen):

Using controller # 2 

Press UP - UP - DOWN - DOWN - LEFT - RIGHT - LEFT - RIGHT - B - A
( If entered correctly you will here a tone )

9 CONTINUES - ( go to the option screen ):

Using controller # 2 

Press UP - X - LEFT - Y - DOWN - B - RIGHT - A - UP - X 
( If done correctly you will here a tone )
After running out of lives you will have 9 continues.

STAGE 1-1 

   The cape sweep attack will take care of the motorcycle clowns.
For thin clowns simply punch and throw them.  Avoid the fire of
the bazooka clown by coming in on an angle and throwing him from
behind.  Attack the fire clown in the same manner. Now collect
the health heart, another one will be in the mailbox.  To defeat
the tall clown stand at a safe distance and jump up and shoot
batarangs at his head.

STAGE 1-2

   Jump up to avoid the fat clown's bounce. By the Christmas tree
stop just to the left of it and you will find that the enemies
continue to come towards you from the left and right. Stay here
and defeat them to rack up points.  

STAGE 1-3     Boss #1 

    Stun clown; jump up when he rolls, then when he stops batarang him and use
test          tubes on him.

STAGE 2-1     

You will see three cans punch them, and collect health and test
tube icons. Avoid the gifts that the thin clowns throw; they
explode.  Attack the juggling clown from behind, walk
towards him at an angle. Use the same technique on the knife
throwers. Collect point and test tube icon from the cans, then
cape sweep the motorcycle rider and collect the health icon.

STAGE 2-2

On the escalator shoot the clowns with batarangs, watch out
for the fat clown. To cross the fire on the floor switch to the
spear gun and aim for the ceiling while continuously pressing
right and the A button.


STAGE 2-3      

Get health and point icons out from the cans. To defeat the sword
eater come in on an angle and  throw him.

Boss #2 Strongman

   Attack him on an angle to avoid his punches, use the cape sweep to clear out
the thin clowns then grab and throw the boss, till he is defeated.

STAGE 3-1       

   On the elevator, windows with the lights on have enemies which will jump out
at you.  when the elevator stops use the bat spear gun and tap the A button
twice to get to the next elevator.

STAGE 3-2       

   When you reach the top of the ceiling you will notice windows
to the right. Jump to the first window ledge and fall straight
down. Look  to the left and collect a test tube.  Now go to the
right, jump up to the window ledge. On the second window ledge,
jump up the use the bat spear  gun. Tap A repeatedly to get to
the red ledge. Now you will encounter a tall clown, collect the
health and test tube icon's. Use the spear gun and continue
right, after the ropes take the elevator to the top of the
building. Use the spear gun to get to the grey ledge.

STAGE 3-3       Boss #3 Catwoman

   Move in the opposite direction when she runs, then approach
her at an angle; throw and punch her to defeat her.

STAGE 4-1       

   There is an assortment of thin and fat clowns. Attack them by punching and
throwing.

STAGE 4-2       

   Fire clowns and sword eaters, attack them at an angle and from behind, then
throw and punch them.

STAGE 4-3       Boss #4 Catwoman

   The easiest way to defeat her in this stage, is by using the bat spear gun
on the ceiling.  Repeatedly tap the A button while moving to the left and
then to the right and then back to the left.  You will automatically kick her
while you do this, and you will take little or no damage while defeating her.

STAGE 4-4        Boss #5 The Penguin

   To defeat him jump and shoot batarangs at him, avoid his umbrellas.

STAGE 5-1        The Batmobile 

   Use the Y button to shoot. To slow down, press down. Watch for a space in
between the motorcycle riders to avoid excessive damage to the batmobile. 
                             
Boss #6 The Campaign Vehicle

   When you reach the campaign vehicle press down on the control pad to slow
down this will cause the grey bombs to explode before they reach the
batmobile. Move left and right to avoid the dynamite. Keep shooting and this
boss will be defeated in no time.       

STAGE 6-1       

   On the circus train there is a "1up" before the first metal beam. Be sure to
jump over the beams. After a while the train will stop.

STAGE 6-2 Boss #7 The Organ grinder

   Come in at him on an angle, and use the cape sweep to trap him on the right
or left side of the screen. Then continue cape sweeping him to keep him
there. If you have mastered this move he will be defeated quickly, with no
damage coming to Batman.

STAGE 7-1       

   More motorcycle, fire, and bomb throwing clowns. Use the cape sweep to help
clear the screen of clowns then throw and punch to defeat them.

STAGE 7-2  Boss #8 The Duckmobile

   Stay to the far right or left to avoid the bombs. Walk under the duckmobile
when it tries to run you over.

STAGE 7-3  Boss #9 The Penguin

   To defeat him you can use your cape sweep to trap him on the
left or right, then continue cape sweeping to defeat him. If you
want more of a challenge attack him at an angle, and throw and
punch him. Use a test tube on him when he flies.
@ENDNODE
@NODE "The Twisted Tales Of Spike McFang Cheat"
                           The Spike Mcfang Cheat!

  Take the Joypad en do this On The Title Screen : Down,b,left,bup,y,right,y
  If You Do This Rigth Than You Must Hear a Chime.
  Now Go Through your castle and defeat the boss, felina. When rudy comes to
  rescue and you go back to the town, take than joypad 2 and now you can
  control rudy!

  nice huh? well have fun... Pinhead/t?
@ENDNODE
@NODE "Tiny Toon Adventures - Buster Busts Loose Walktrough"
Tiny Toon Adventures - Buster Busts Loose

Level 1:  
   The first obstacles you will encounter in the hallway are the lockers.  Use
your spin attack to deter any mice then use your dash button to slide
underneath the staircase for an extra heart and full power up.  After
climbing the stairs, get ready to run.  With some timely jumping, it is
possible to dash through the entire section.  The library is next.  Step on
the red buttons to  make the book cases move closer together and use the dash
button.  After sliding down the trap door, use your spin attack to defeat the
mini boss and obtain the key.  Before using the elevator, check for power
ups.  After you reach the top, use your dash button and jump to easily pick
up a few stars before facing Dizzy.  To defeat Dizzy, stand in the lower left
hand corner when Dizzy is spinning.  When Dizzy stops spinning, he will
follow you.  Enter the elevator ahead of him and jump back down to the
bottom.  Wait until just before he walks over the food and jump up to make
the food airborne.  Do this ten times and Dizzy will fall asleep.

Level 2:
   Hit the dash button to knock all the barrels over.  Repeat this and be
careful not to get hit by the men in the windows.  When jumping rope, press
the jump button when the rope passes Bug Eyes.  To avoid the crows flying
over the horses, use your spin attack.  When you enter the inn, use your spin
attack immediately to defeat the dog.  Be careful to not get hit by a falling
chandelier.  The best way to avoid the falling barrels is to walk straight up
the stairs very quickly.  After meeting Montana Max, get ready for the train
ride of your life.  First, use your spin attack to defeat the two barely
visible enemies on the caboose.  Next, you must avoid four nets, however, if
you do get caught, use your dash button for a quick escape.  Use your dash
button to run up the side of the train car, use your spin attack to defeat
the enemy at the top and get ready to dash.  You might have some trouble with
this section, it requires perfect timing on the jumps and even if you do make
it, it will only be by the skin of your teeth.  If you make it over the
mountain you will be back on the train.  After you are back on the train the
bridge will start collapsing.  You must time your jumps from one car to the
next perfectly.  The best advice for this section is for you to wait until
the car you are on almost falls off the screen.  After all of this you will
be back on the train.  Defeat the two mini bosses by using your spin attack.
 Next up is the man with the expandable wand.  To defeat him the best thing
to do is just attack him.  He takes five hits to destroy.  Next up, after
jumping the pieces of wood is the polar bear.  Jump on him twice to defeat
him.  You are finally nearing the end.  The first two smoke stacks on the
train s engine are relatively easy.  Hit them with your spin attack four
times each.  The big smoke stack takes five hits.  The last thing you have to
do on this level is press the button rapidly to get away from the train.
   
Level 3:
   When starting out it is very important to use your spin attack to defeat the
ghosts.  Before you pass the welcome sign make sure to run up the walls for
full power ups.  Next you will be on the spring boards.  When you are on this
section, make sure to use your spin attack while in the air for maximum
effectiveness.  Also, look up a wall for a free guy.  After that, climb the
ladders up to the swinging hammer section.  Completing this level requires a
lot of timely jumping.  One hint I can give you is that Babs is on the top.
 Once you reach Babs you will have to defeat the mad scientist s machine.  In
order to destroy the machine, blow up the bolts that the robot throws at you
by using your spin attack.

Level 4:
   Level four is basically self explanatory.  The best advice for this level is
to try and figure out the pattern in which the defense comes at you for big
gains.  Score a touchdown and this level is over.


Level 5:
   Level five starts out with some tricky balloon jumping.  Try and stay ahead
of the exploding balloons.  The next section requires you to jump from
balloon to balloon.  Timing is essential because the balloons start to sink
the moment you touch them.  Look for the free guy in this section.  The next
section is Buster on the Blimp.  Use your drop kick to get through this
section fairly easily.  Next is the pinball section.  Concentrate on guiding
Buster into anything that moves.  When Buster is falling down, make sure to
guide him towards the flippers.  There are three stages to this.  The first
stage involves collecting five blue balls from the bubbles to open a platform
so you can reach the next section.  The next stage involves Buster clearing
out a bunch of multicolored spheres.  Once he does that he is transported to
the third stage in which all you have to do is guide buster into the port
hole at the top of the section.

Level 6:
   Start out by using your dash button to climb the walls.  Make your way to
the left and find the ladder.  Climb the ladder and grab the life icon.  Look
for the full life and extra guy power ups.  Look in the upper left hand
corner for the key you need.  The next section is the space battlefield.
 Hide behind any object left standing to protect yourself from the nuke
blasts.  In order to defeat the laser gun you must jump the laser when it
sweeps past the floor and use your spin kick to bump the alien off the laser.
 When you bump the alien the laser will hit the alien.  Do this five times
and Babs is saved.  
@ENDNODE
